research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Combes, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which is a mayor-commission type. Mayor Silvestre Garcia was sworn in on May 16, 2023. Commissioners Olga H. Montes, Carlos Cordova, and Jose J. Herrera were re-elected or newly elected on May 13, 2024. Commissioners Mary A. David and Ann Forbes were elected or re-elected on May 6, 2023.
